Package: ICellbioRpy
Type: Package
Title: Read and Convert 1CellBio Results and Stereo-seq GEF Files to Seurat, SingleCellExperiment and H5AD
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    c(
      person("1Cellbio", "X", email = "your@email",
             role = c("aut"))
    )
URL: https://github.com/1-Cellbio/ICellbioRpy
BugReports: https://github.com/1-Cellbio/ICellbioRpy/issues
Description: Tools to convert 1CellBio results (ZIP) and Stereo-seq GEF files to Seurat, SingleCellExperiment, and H5AD formats, with comprehensive support for spatial transcriptomics including cell border visualization. Includes memory-efficient sparse matrix preservation and interconversion between R and Python single-cell formats.
